{"id": "1335024504027746357", "channel_id": "1326453691527594035", "author_id": "714574912030900334", "author_name": "darkmagicsolo", "content": "Hi there! I wanna build Sanga, any advice on how you’d do it?", "timestamp": "2025-01-31T23:10:45.316000+00:00"}
